wiki.content:
"Domino" is a song by British singer Jessie J, recorded for their debut album, Who You Are. It was composed by Jessica Cornish, Lukasz Gottwald, Claude Kelly, Max Martin, Walter Henry, and produced by Dr. Luke and Martin. Launched on August 29, 2011 on the iTunes Store, serving as the second single from the artist in the United States, following the "Price Tag".
